# Exit Prompted
Fire this whenever a user used the words "Buy/Purchase", "Home Depot", or "Customer Service"


## Javascript Code
```js
window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
dataLayer.push({
  "event": "Exit Prompted",
  "exitType": "Intent to purchase/Intent to speak to agent"
}
});
```


##Dynamic Variable Definitions
| Path     | Definition | Possible Values | Data Type |
|----------|----------|----------|----------|
| exitType | If a user mentions "Buy/Purchase" or "Home Depot", return "Intent to purchase", If a user mentions "Customer Service" |  | String |
|  |  | ||
